  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5703990">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5703990/" class="title-link">译文惨不忍睹</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5703990"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1346689/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1346689-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1346689/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">1997xhp</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-18"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-18 22:54:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5703990_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  内容五星，翻译两星。我一般不会对译文说三道四，除非其到了正常人忍耐的极限。此书是我看过的继天雷滚滚的《兴登堡自传》之后的又一本垃圾。抛去满页的英语句式不提，令人摸不清东西的语句几乎每页都出现。例子懒得举了，不信可以看看59页开头，望脑筋急转弯高手为我指点一下...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5703990/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
