  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5744639">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5744639/" class="title-link">总之就是对逻辑有疑问</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5744639"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tomas.psi/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u37744252-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tomas.psi/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">半嶋·不响</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-01-17"
      class="main-meta">2013-01-17 16:07:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5744639_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  优点不说了，说说缺点。我不知道是翻译的问题还是原来作者的问题，这本书在处理某些年代以及史实时，逻辑显得有些草率。阅读下来，我认为翻译问题是该书存在的一个弊病，虽无原文对照，然书中出现的很多断句错误以及状语错误已经出卖了译者的水平，这着实让读者费一番神。另外...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5744639/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5744639_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5744639_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
